						<td>
						<p ALIGN="LEFT" class="subtitle">The Sudden (to us) Success of Daed Toolworks
						<font size="2">
						<span style="font-weight: 400">by Christopher Schwarz.&nbsp;
						</span></font>
						<font style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: 400">Copyright 
						2011.&nbsp; Originally appeared in the
						<a target="_blank" href="../../../../0_0-Ads/z_Source/zz_Advert/z_track/FineToolJourn-track.asp">
						Fine Tool Journal </a></font></td>
						<td align="right" width="95" height="26" valign="bottom">
						<span style="font-size: 8pt">
						<a href="../../cSchwarz-index.asp">
						<img border="0" src="../../../../0_xGlobal-incl/0_img-Nav/arrowBack.jpg" width="24" height="24"></a>
						<b>1 of 2</b> 
